The paper deals with the task of semantic segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves iterative optimization of a segmentation network, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method also involves the use of saliency maps, which are commonly used in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) tasks.
